sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant UI as Next.js UI
    participant Server as API Route
    participant AI as OpenAI

    User->>UI: Type message + send
    UI->>Server: POST /api/chat
    Server->>AI: streamText request
    AI-->>Server: Streaming response
    Server-->>UI: Real-time data relay
    UI-->>User: Display on screen
